modName: TroubleMakers Clothing - UNPB UNP BBP BBPx TBBP MTM HDT-PE Female Body Replacer
summary:
Barkeeper/Chef Tunic/Tavern(Wench)/Sandals UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx mesh conversion/edit with working weight slider. Standalone and Replacers. Added Transparent versions. Added SFW bikinis Main body Replacer for UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx
Home for UNPB 2.2-2.4 and MTM bodies also UNP-BBP bodies with HDT-PE patch
descriptionHtml:
==============================================================================================================================================

TroubleMakers Clothing

==============================================================================================================================================

Standalone Craftable Version at forge in hide 2.62
Standalone Craftable Version at Tanning Rack in hide 2.63

Multiple versions of each

Arm Cuffs

Bodice

Sleeveless Bodice

Long Skirt

Long Covering Skirt

Short Skirt

Short Covering Skirt

Short Skirt with Apron

Tavern Wench (only one version)

Sandals (only one version)

Belt (only one version)

Panties

Thong

ST = Semi Transparent
T = Transparent

Bodice uses Biped 32
Skirt uses Biped 52
Belt uses Biped 47
Panties/Thong uses Biped 45
Arm Cuffs uses Biped 34

Same biped values that Brokefoot used for his Mashup.

Included textures by dikr, PanTast, MrTroubleMaker, Backsteppo, dimon99 and Bethesda

=====================================================================================================================================

Single package consists of Barkeeper/Alt, Chef's Tunic, Tavern Wench and Wedding Sandals meshes, all are replacers. Just neatly packaged up into one file. In optional files.

Barkeeper Chef's Tunic

Added Transparent version in miscl files.
A new transparent texture version. These great new textures are by dikr
Another version that uses default textures use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11709]UNP-Barkeeper-Slightly-Transparent by PanTast[/url]

Chef semi/transparent texture by MrTroubleMaker

Added
Barkeeper/Alt Barkeeper/Chef with Alt Skirt over Bodice in miscl files.

0005b6a1
0006ff38

0001bc82

Wedding Sandals

00088958

Tavern Wench

000d191f

I created Small (optional) esp that deselects Biped object

35 Amulet
36 Ring

on Barkeeper/AltBarkeeper/Chef's Tunic
To allow proper wearing (showing) of Amulet (necklace) and Ring.
Bethesda had them selected for some reason and those two items wouldn't always show.
If you have another mod that edits these 3 clothes, it probably will conflict.

====================================================================================================================================

UNPB Bodies - 2.2 - 2.4 and MTM bodies

====================================================================================================================================


[img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/20227-1-1373705934.jpg[/img]
The UNP Blessed Body increases the maximum size of the breasts for the UNP Body. The end result is comparable to CBBE in cup-size while still maintaining the details we UNPers love. Nothing is changed but the breast size, and the shape is still in line with the latest UNP breasts (B2), just increased.

Feel free to add pictures of this Body or the Clothing/Armor. I'm not the best picture taker, and its great to see how it looks in others games. Also it will help promote the Body.

I'm placing the body files in Update and Old, neither is being used as update or old. I'm just using these categories to help distinguish the body files

[img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/20227-2-1373705934.jpg[/img]

[color=pink][b][center]Installation UNPB NMM Installer[/center][/b][/color]
Run in NMM, No other files are needed.It includes all Body Versions 2.2 2.2p 2.2x 2.4 and sfw. If you would like another texture or animation, there are a lot of mods to choose from, UNP, UNPB.

[color=pink][b][center]Installation UNPB and UNP NMM Installer MTM Bodies[/center][/b][/color]
Run in NMM, No other files are needed. It includes all UNP/UNPB MTM Body Versions - 2.3 No bounce, L Bouncy, M More Bounce, X Heavy Bounce, G Gravity Bounce, T TBBP Bounce, B2 Bounce and SFW. Includes Vanilla scale Skeleton that supports TBBP/BBP/SOS also it is already patched for the arm fix. Also includes BBP and TBBP animations and Textures. If you would like another Texture, Skeleton or Animation, there are a lot of mods to choose from, UNP, UNPB.

[color=pink][b][center]Installation UNPB UNP MTM Bodies HDT-PE patch NMM Installer[/center][/b][/color]
Run in NMM, This installer adds breast and hand physics collisions to the player character (see the gif) three values available. It is intended as a patch to an installed version of either UNPB Body NMM Installer or UNPB MTM Bodies and UNP MTM Bodies NMM Installer (run either of those first then overwrite with this patch). It adds the collision physics to the breasts and hands by adding a string to female head mesh that HDT-PE uses. So it should work with any clothing or armour you place on your character. It also includes HDT-PE enabled Ring and Necklace (for followers).
Attention - you need to have v14.28 HDT-PE installed first, otherwise this package wont work! - Attention.
Attention - Altering the scale of the  breast bones may cause issues with the collision filters. - Attention.
Please read UNPB-HDTPE.txt in the package for information/credits and custom race support.

[color=pink][b][center]Installation UNPB Standard without BBP and SFW[/center][/b][/color]
Download UNPB 2.2 Body and drop the data folder into your skyrim directory. This version needs textures from a UNP/UNPB mod.
[color=pink][b][center][/center][/b][/color]
[color=pink][b][center]Installation for UNP-BBP MTM B2 also UNPB-BBP MTM L, M, X, G and SFW[/center][/b][/color]
Download and drop the data folder into your skyrim directory. Uses included Vanilla scale Skeleton that is already patched for the arm fix - Needs UNP/UNPB textures and animations [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34508]360 Walk and Run Plus[/url].

[color=pink][b][center]Installation for UNPB-TBBP MTM T and SFW[/center][/b][/color]
Download and drop the data folder into your skyrim directory. Uses included Vanilla scale Skeleton that supports TBBP/BBP and SOS also it is already patched for the arm fix - Needs UNP/UNPB textures and TBBP animations [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/34713]TBBP animation of Dragonfly[/url].

[color=yellow]Fore has a integrated patch for CHSBHC-BBP arm fix, this also will patch UNPB-BBP ( 2.2p 2.2x and 2.4 ). You can download [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11811]FNIS 3.x.x -Always necessary files[/url]. Recommended to use it.[/color]

[img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/20227-4-1373705934.jpg[/img]
Use the search function for UNPB to find mods using this body.

UNPB bodies for Temptress race users are here
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22166]Brokefoot UNP Mashup Compilation UNPB BBP BBPx Conversion[/url]

[img]http://static-2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/20227-3-1373705934.jpg[/img]

[color=yellow]"Halp! My huskarls aren't jiggling!"[/color]
Install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35155/]Correct Gender Animations by thefinn[/url], Use before you become Thane

[color=yellow]"Halp! My Orc Female isn't jiggling!"[/color]
There are a couple mods that change Orc race Females to use female animations. Try [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25495]
Orc female idle FIX[/url] or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/16392]Feminine Female Orcs[/url] or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35155/]Correct Gender Animations by thefinn[/url]

[color=yellow]"Halp! My High and Wood Elf Female clothing/armour CTD!"[/color]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33470/]High and Wood elf skeleton fix by drywater509[/url]

[color=yellow]"Will this add muscles like in the picture?"[/color]
No. Muscles come from mods like [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/downloads/file.php?id=13377]this one[/url]. The UNPB Body simply increases the breast size of the standard UNP body.

[color=yellow]"I have a custom texture/normal installed, will this affect that?"[/color]
Nope, it's optional in the installer version.

[color=yellow]"Does this work with skinny UNP?" [/color]
no

[color=yellow]"Will this clip with my UNP armors?"[/color]
No. Armor meshes contain their own body mesh so using this as your base won't affect anything you wear.

[color=yellow]"Are there any armors for this?" [/color]
Yes!

[color=yellow]"I installed BBP version but when I wear ____ armor my boobs don't bounce!"[/color]
An armor has to be weighted and include the skeleton for BBP, which requires importing it to a 3d program and making it compatible. So only armors with BBP in the title will bounce.

[color=yellow]"Can you make a CBBE version?"[/color]
What?

[color=yellow]"I disagree with this mod."[/color]
No one is forced to dl. Dimon's awesome original version remains untouched on his mod page.

[color=yellow]"Modders package"[/color]
There is a Modder's Resource package for the Body files, just link back to this page for the credits. If you want to make an armor for this body or port an armor to the UNPB body, feel free. No need to ask my permission. Basically the same rules apply as if you were working with the regular UNP body.
Clothing meshes/textures are not modder's resource and need my permission.

====================================================================================================================================


SFW bikinis Main body Replacer in Old Files

This is a conversion of dimon99's SFW Bikinis for UNPB/UNPB-BBP/UNPB-BBPx This is only Mesh and weight changes for the UNPB body type.

Overwrite the two mesh files for the body type you want.

You can get the Chainmail textures from
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/45]Obligatory Chainmail Bikini by Rekicker[/url]
Or HD textures from
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/23875]HD UNPB and UNP SFW Undergarment Redone by crispiniscool[/url] another [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24747]High Definition Leather Undergarments by crispiniscool[/url]
or use the texture from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709]dimon99's SFW bikinis[/url]

====================================================================================================================================


Standalone works nicely with Brokefoots mashup and dikr's Bouncy Bodices
